      "description": "A utility class providing HTTP client operations (GET, POST, PUT, DELETE) with support for both HTTP and HTTPS protocols. It wraps Apache HttpClient to provide simplified methods for making HTTP requests with customizable headers, query parameters, and request bodies.",
      "functions": [
        "doGet",
        "doPost (form)",
        "doPost (string body)",
        "doPost (byte array)",
        "doPut (string body)",
        "doPut (byte array)",
